5
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:17,800
Mr, Mu, have you really made up your mind?

6
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:22,920
Anyway, my lord also said

7
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:24,520
if you refused to listen to advice

8
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,728
and insisted on going,
you would bear the consequences,

9
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:32,136
Then please thank your lord for me, Move aside,

10
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,640
Mr, Mu San has arrived,

11
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:54,320
Now, it's going to be fun,

12
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,520
San, following the merchants,

13
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:38,320
your journey was very arduous,

14
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,488
But it doesn't matter,

15
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:44,440
From now on,
Chongyu will surely take good care of you all,

16
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,880
Just now, Minister said after passing Guazhou,

17
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:53,920
