19
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,280
Our caravan's camels walk slowly,

20
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,912
With many people and goods,
we cannot take the Ohaido,

21
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,260
So when we reach Xizhou,

22
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:04,000
we will part ways with Minister,

23
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,080
So what?

24
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:22,800
San, I will prepare the best horse for you

25
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,440
