26
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,504
But…

27
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,336
Sanniang,

28
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,200
Without listening to your dissuasion,

29
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:48,180
I was wrong to go to the banquet,

30
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:49,620
But I could have anticipated

31
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:52,760
Minister Qu actually has such a strange hobby,

32
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,600
Jiu, as the Senior Official of Xizhou,

33
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,420
Y-You must have a way,

34
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,920
You can't stand by and do nothing,

35
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:07,480
Shouyue, you have to come up
with a plan for your cousin,

36
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:11,592
As for the plan, there is one, But…

37
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:17,420
No, if I tell you this idea,

38
00:05:17,420 --> 00:05:18,940
you'll definitely think
that I'm trying to harm you,

39
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:20,000
Jiu, you can rest assured,

40
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,820
As long as I can get rid of
Minister's entanglements,

41
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:23,160
whatever you say, I'll do,

42
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:28,620
The Qu family has a deep-rooted foundation
in the Xizhou,

43
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:29,760
As for me, I've just arrived here,

44
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,760
We haven't even entered Xizhou yet,

45
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,480
What if we offend Minister before that?
What do we do then?

46
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,640
Shouyue, San is like my own brother,

47
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,640
Please help him,

48
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:42,408
Hurry up,

49
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:48,640
B-B-Brother-in-law,
please help your elder brother,

50
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:52,840
What are you calling me?

51
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:59,320
Brother-in-law, please give me some advice,

52
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,792
Alright,

53
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:08,280
Cousin, rest assured,
Just do as I say tomorrow,

54
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:11,280
I will naturally help you
get rid of Minister's entanglements,

55
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:17,040
Well then, I'll take my leave first,

56
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,736
Take care,

57
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,480
You're up to no good again, aren't you?

58
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,840
Qu Chongyu is always testing me,

59
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:40,000
Then I can give him back his own way,

60
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,800
Maybe I can kill two birds with one stone,

61
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:45,600
I can help Mu San break the blockade,

62
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,960
And also send this rival in love away,
isn't that wonderful?

63
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,240
I knew your motives weren't pure,

64
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:56,720
Your beauty would put the flowers to shame,

65
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,440
To have such a cousin by your side,

66
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,640
I really can't be at ease,

67
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,140
This is very good,

68
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:06,640
Since we have to put on a performance
for Qu Chongyu to watch,

69
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:09,440
then I shall continue to
play the role of ignorant and shallow shrew,

70
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,200
Then I will cooperate with you,

71
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,560
instilling a fearful, submissive husband image
deep into people's hearts,

72
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,440
I am a shrew,

73
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,400
I'm henpecked,

74
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,448
Listen to me, okay?

75
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,704
Okay,

76
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,640
It's not a solution for me
to keep hiding in the carriage,

77
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,680
Liuli, can you urge Shouyue for me?

78
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,400
We've already reached Guazhou,

79
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,400
What about his idea?

80
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,960
Shouyue, you're so magnanimous,

81
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,840
Mu San and Madam Kudi get along well,

82
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,280
Don't you mind?

83
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:32,680
Bah, that dead peacock always talks nonsense,

84
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,080
Minister, you misunderstood,

85
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:38,000
San, like my wife's biological brother,
has joined under my command,

86
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:40,640
He should receive extra care,

87
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:46,220
But there are many people from An Family
in this merchant family,

88
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:49,240
Why do you view San differently?

89
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:54,240
It seems
Minister pays special attention to San,

90
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,720
Then I'll do a favor,

91
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,800
How about letting San attend to Minister?

92
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:08,000
Gu, stop it,

93
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,824
Hush,

94
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,736
San,

95
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:16,040
